\id GEN Meriam Mer - draft material - not consultant checked 
\toc2 ZENESIS 
\toc1 ZENESIS 
\mt1 ZENESIS  
\ip draft by Ken Passi Peter Wickham SIL Mer Feb 1987  
\c 1  
\d MIZMIZ 1  
\p
\v 1 Agraretge Agudide kotor a gesep daratagemda,  
\v 2 able gesep ge irdireder orwaikak a lukak. Able muimui karem ge gair lu narimlare kupkupi detrapeder abi tumge, a Agudira sasrim atatmirer tumem able nige.  
\v 3 Agud eudim etkaret, “Bi obakaeret”, ege bi bakaerti  
\v 4 Agudira serer barki nalu e dasmeri.  
\v 5 E eudim bi detakemuda kupkupilam, a able bi nei itkiri Gerger a kupkupi nei itkiri Ki. Ki a idim ge kikem gerger irdireder.  
\v 6 Agud ga etkaret, “Kes obatreret eipuge ko ni wanakesmuda neis utebem” - ege akaida.  
\v 7 Agudide able kes ikaida arem ni detakemuda seplelam.  
\v 8 E able kes nei itkiri Mi. Ki a idim ga 2 gerger irdireder.  
\v 9 Agud eudim etkaret, “Able ni pe milam sepge egmedi (wataba) okokise waetami ya wayakai ged wedaketi.” - a ege akaida.  
\v 10 E able ged nei itkiri Gesep a able ni ge netat utebge etami, e nei itkiri Gur. A Agudira serer barki nalu e dasmeri.  
\v 11 Agud ga etkaret, “Gesep turum weud gair tonar lunege; luneg wi no kep waeslare a able lu yaba kep wadaragri muige yaba ageg” - a ege bakerda.  
\v 12 Able gesep turum eudi gair tonar lunege a Agudira serer barki nalu e dasmeri.  
\v 13 Ki a idim ga 3 gerger irdireder.  
\v 14 Agud eudim etkaret, “Mige bi obakaertare ko kepu wanakwaelei gerger a ki, a ko waetomeretlare kerker, gerger a urut;  
\v 15 wi zorom obazimurwa mige ko bi waiswelare gesepem” - a ege bakerda.  
\v 16 Agudide neis au bi dararsiri - lim ko abra sasrim wadike gergerge a meb ko abra sasrim wadike kige.  
\v 17 E wer gako dararsirda. Agudide able bi idagi mige ko gesep bi waiswerlare,  
\v 18 sasrim yaba wadaragri gergerem a kiem, a ko kepu wanakweilei bi a kupkupi. Agudira serer barki nalu e dasmeri.  
\v 19 Ki a idim ga 4 gerger irdireder.  
\v 20 Agud ga etkaret, “Ni turum weud gair tonar large a able mikes turum weud mi eburge.”  
\v 21 Agudide daratagemda gair tonar au gur ebur gair tonar ebur pe able gurge waurder a gair tonar mi ebur. Agudira serer barki nalu e dasmeri.  
\v 22 Agudide yabi gair werkabem nakerda a able ni ebur daratagerda ko nosik yaba waeprao gurge a ni wadamiare.  
\v 23 Ki a idim ga 5 gerger irdireder.  
\v 24 Agud ga etkaret, “Gesepide gair tonar gesep ebur waeprao: uteb a ad ebur, aule a kebile” - a ege akaida.  
\v 25 Agudide eudim yabi gair darasirda, a abra serer barki nalu e dasmeri.  
\v 26 A Agudide eudim detauti, “Pe irdi mi le dararsirei; wi wadaralei merbi kaise a merbi orwaiorwai. Yaba yako sasrim wadarake large, mi eburge a gair gesep eburge, uteb ebur a ad ebur aule a kebile.  
\v 27 Agudide eudim le daratagmi yabi nakaida ko abi kaise wadaralei. E yabi kimyar a koskir daratagmi,  
\v 28 werkabem nakaida, a detauti, “Mitkar omaskir ko waba wanagri wayakai waba nosik ya waurder kemerkemer gesepge a gesep sir wadamilare. Ka wabi dikweida able sasrimge ko waba wanake large, ni eburge, a gair ad gesep eburge.  
\v 29 Ka emetu dararsirda gair tonar kep a kurup lewer wabim arwem;  
\v 30 a gair gesep eburem a mi eburem ka sogi a lamlam luneg dararsirda yabim lewerem” - a ege akaida.  
\v 31 Agudide gair lu darasmerda ge e dararsirda, ege abra au serer barki. Ki a idim ga 6 gerger irdireder.   